- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper uses natural language processing techniques (word2vec) to model musical context, which can be considered as a form of computational linguistics. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses a machine learning model (word2vec) to capture musical context. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper deals with capturing and modeling complex musical context, which can be considered as a form of information retrieval.
